watashitachi ni asu no jiyuu to 
yuuki wo kureru wa Sakura no hanabiratachi ga saku koro 
dokoka de dareka ga kitto inotteru 
atarashii sekai no DOA wo 
jibun no sono te de hiraku koto Kenkashite denwashite naita ko to atta ne 
